Reason: the C++ shims in this directory (mesen_step.cpp, mesen_candidate.cpp,
and the NBA equivalents) include Mesen2 and NanoBoyAdvance headers and link
against their objects. Both upstream projects are GPL-3.0, so this shim
layer is GPL-3.0 as well.

